citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:45 AM on 6
August 2025. The inspector attempted to contact the licensee/registrant by phone, waited 30 minutes and called a second
time - left a message both times. Failure to provide access to the facility, animals, and records for inspection is a serious
violation of the AWA and regulations. Failure to comply may result in enforcement action.
End Section

Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.

time - left a message both times. Failure to provide access to the facility, animals, and records for inspection is a serious 
violation of the AWA and regulations. Failure to comply may result in enforcement action.
